original: Forsell, Axel Daniel, apotekare. Lilla Edet, f. 28/4/92 i Holm, Älvsb. <1., av järnv :itj :m. Fredrik Andersson o. Anna Forsell G. m. Ina Carlsson. Barn: Erik f. 20, Gudrun 26. — Farm. kand. 18, apot:ex. 23. Elev v. apot. i Söderhamn, anst. där, v. apot. Fenix i Nyköp., apot. i Biilingsfors, Kronan i Upps. 24-29, Korpen i Gbg 29-41, priv. å apot. i Lilla Edet sed. 41.
translated: Forsell, Axel Daniel, pharmacist. Born on April 28, 1892 in Holm, Älvsborg County to parents Fredrik Andersson and Anna Forsell, who were engaged in the iron industry. Married to Ina Carlsson. Children: Erik (born 1920) and Gudrun (born 1926). Graduated as a pharmaceutical candidate in 1918 and became a licensed pharmacist in 1923. Worked as an apprentice at a pharmacy in Söderhamn and later became an employee there. He also worked at the Fenix pharmacy in Nyköping, the Biilingsfors pharmacy, the Kronan pharmacy in Uppsala from 1924 to 1929, and at the Korpen pharmacy in Gothenburg from 1929 to 1941. From 1941 he had a private pharmacy in Lilla Edet.
